{"type":"message","id":"4df88b4c","parentId":"2b047269","timestamp":"2026-04-10T22:56:50.341Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Ah, der Ordner heißt \"migration-skill\", nicht \"safe-migration\". Und er wurde bereits verschoben (Timestamp 00:40). Jetzt sollte ich ihn in die Registry eintragen, damit er vollständig aktiviert ist.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Der Ordner heißt `migration-skill` und ist bereits im `skills/` Ordner. Jetzt trage ich ihn in die Registry ein..."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_lQaeR49FirE5NnLex7Lkd3jo","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:/Users/andre/.openclaw/workspace/skills/migration-skill/SKILL.md","limit":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":271,"output":131,"cacheRead":143616,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":144018,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775861804435}}
{"type":"message","id":"62260b17","parentId":"4df88b4c","timestamp":"2026-04-10T22:56:50.357Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_lQaeR49FirE5NnLex7Lkd3jo","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: safe-migration\nversion: \"1.0.0\"\ndescription: |\n  Foolproof migration assistant with safety checks, validation, and quality assurance.\n  Prevents data loss through backups, dry-runs, incremental batches, and automated validation.\nauthor: Andrew\nsource: Based on lessons learned from vault migration failures\ntags: [migration, safety, backup, validation, quality]\n---\n\n# Safe Migration Skill\n\nFoolproof migration with comprehensive safety checks and quality assurance.\n\n## When to Use\n\n- Migrating files between directories or systems\n- Converting file formats\n- Restructuring vaults or projects\n- Any operation that could result in data loss\n\n## Safety Principles\n\n1. **Backup FIRST** - Always backup before any changes\n2. **Dry-Run** - Test with 3 files before full migration\n3. **Incremental** - Max 5 files per batch\n4. **Validate** - Automated checks after each batch\n5. **Never Delete Originals** - Until validation is confirmed\n\n\n[111 more lines in file. Use offset=31 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775861810351}}
