bsidian Meta | 44 | LOW - Plugin configs, etc. |\n\n---\n\n## Critical Findings\n\n### 1. HIGH VALUE: Technical Specifications\n\n| File | Location | Relevance | Action |\n|------|----------|-----------|--------|\n| **OPENCLAW_CLAWCODE_INTEGRATION_MASTERPLAN.md** | `Kimi_Agent_OpenClaw GitHub/` | CRITICAL | MIGRATE to 03-Knowledge/References/ |\n| **AI_AGENT_WORK_INSTRUCTION.md** | Root | HIGH - Edit-tool fix | MIGRATE to 03-Knowledge/How-To/ |\n| **SUBAGENT_*.md** (5 files) | `Kimi_Agent_OpenClaw GitHub/` | HIGH - Subagent specs | MIGRATE to 03-Knowledge/References/ |\n| **harness_redesign_specification.md** | Root | MEDIUM | REVIEW - may overlap with existing |\n| **OpenClaw_Harness_Diagnosis.md** | Root | MEDIUM | REVIEW - technical diagnosis |\n| **Master Rework Documents** (6 files) | `Master Rework 06.04.2026/` | HIGH | ALREADY MIGRATED? Check duplicates |\n\n### 2. HIGH VALUE: PowerShell Scripts & Modules\n\n| File | Purpose | Relevance | Action |\n|------|---------|-----------|--------|\n| **sync-openclaw-to-obsidian.ps1** | Bidirectional sync | HIGH | COMPARE with current sync script |\n| **drift-detection.ps1** | Config drift detection | HIGH | MERGE with existing |\n| **ecc-stability.ps1** | System stability checks | HIGH | REVIEW - may enhance current |\n| **auto-backup.ps1** | Automated backups | MEDIUM | Check if better than current |\n| **DataviewQuery.psm1** | Dataview query builder | HIGH | UNIQUE - migrate to scripts/ |\n| **Encryption.psm1** | API key encryption | HIGH | COMPARE with current |\n| **MermaidGenerator.psm1** | Diagram generation | HIGH | ALREADY HAVE? Check overlap |\n| **SecureCredential.psm1** | Credential management | HIGH | REVIEW for integration |\n| **ErrorHandler.psm1** | Error handling | MEDIUM | Check quality |\n| **Logging.psm1** | Logging utilities | MEDIUM | Check if needed |\n\n### 3. TEMPLATES (Check for Improvements)\n\n| File | Current Status | Action |\n|------|----------------|--------|\n| Session-Template.md | Have