md** → 03-Knowledge/References/\n2. **SUBAGENT_*.md** (all 5) → 03-Knowledge/References/\n3. **AI_AGENT_WORK_INSTRUCTION.md** → 03-Knowledge/How-To/\n4. **DataviewQuery.psm1** → 00-Meta/Scripts/ecc-framework/\n5. **SecureCredential.psm1** → 00-Meta/Scripts/ecc-framework/\n\n### B) COMPARE & DECIDE (Potential Improvements)\n1. All Templates - compare with current versions\n2. All Scripts - compare functionality\n3. drift-detection.ps1 vs current\n4. Encryption.psm1 vs current\n\n### C) REVIEW FOR PARTIAL MERGE\n1. area-development.md + area-research.md (old versions)\n2. Configuration files (YAML) - may have useful settings\n\n### D) IGNORE\n1. All .obsidian/ configuration\n2. EXAMPLE_ files (templates)\n3. node_modules or package.json files\n4. Workspace state files\n\n---\n\n## Next Steps\n\n**WAITING FOR USER DECISION:**\n\nPlease review this analysis and decide:\n\n1. **Should I proceed with Phase 4** (Integration Decision) for the HIGH priority items?\n2. **Which files do you want me to compare first** (current vs. old)?\n3. **Any specific files you want to exclude** from migration?\n4. **Should I create a detailed migration plan** before executing?\n\n**Recommended approach:** Batch-by-batch with your GO after each batch.\n\n---\n\n*Analysis complete. Ready for Phase 4 (Integration Decision) and Phase 5 (Validation).*","file_path":"C:/Users/andre/.openclaw/workspace/tmp/vault-analysis-phase3.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":110893,"output":2031,"cacheRead":33792,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":146716,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775862900385}}
