{"type":"message","id":"30989408","parentId":"84aee76a","timestamp":"2026-04-10T23:30:11.175Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Der Nutzer möchte, dass ich mit Schritt 1 (Backup) beginne. Ich soll sofort Bescheid geben, wenn ich Fragen habe oder unsicher bin.\n\nIch erstelle einen Backup-Ordner und kopiere die 5 Dateien dorthin.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Ausführe Schritt 1: Safety-Backup..."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_VJZuGH8JL6MfI20DnDqVbQhI","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Schritt 1: Safety-Backup für Batch 1\n$timestamp = Get-Date -Format \"yyyyMMdd_HHmmss\"\n$backupPath = \"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\SecondBrain\\00-Meta\\Backups\\BATCH1_$timestamp\"\n$sourcePath = \"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\vault-archive\\Main_Obsidian_Vault\"\n\n# Backup-Ordner erstellen\nNew-Item -Path $backupPath -ItemType Directory -Force | Out-Null\n\n# Die 5 Batch-1 Dateien identifizieren und kopieren\n$batch1Files = @(\n    \"Kimi_Agent_OpenClaw GitHub\\OPENCLAW_CLAWCODE_INTEGRATION_MASTERPLAN.md\",\n    \"Kimi_Agent_OpenClaw GitHub\\SUBAGENT_COMPACTION_SPEC.md\",\n    \"Kimi_Agent_OpenClaw GitHub\\SUBAGENT_CONVERSATION_RUNTIME_SPEC.md\",\n    \"Kimi_Agent_OpenClaw GitHub\\SUBAGENT_PERMISSIONS_SPEC.md\",\n    \"Kimi_Agent_OpenClaw GitHub\\SUBAGENT_SSE_STREAMING_SPEC.md\"\n)\n\n$results = @()\nforeach ($file in $batch1Files) {\n    $source = Join-Path $sourcePath $file\n    if (Test-Path $source) {\n        $dest = Join-Path $backupPath ($file.Replace(\"\\\", \"_\"))\n        Copy-Item -Path $source -Destination $dest -Force\n        $size = (Get-Item $source).Length\n        $results += [PSCustomObject]@{\n            Datei = $file\n            Status = \"OK\"\n            GroesseBytes = $size\n            BackupPfad = $dest\n        }\n        Write-Host \"OK: $file ($size Bytes)\"\n    } else {\n        $results += [PSCustomObject]@{\n            Datei = $file\n            Status = \"FEHLER - NICHT GEFUNDEN\"\n            GroesseBytes = 0\n            BackupPfad = \"\"\n        }\n        Write-Host \"FEHLER: $file nicht gefunden!\"\n    }\n}\n\n# Ergebnis speichern\n$results | Export-Csv -Path \"$backupPath\\BACKUP_MANIFEST.csv\" -NoTypeInformation\n\nWrite-Host \"`n=== BACKUP ERSTELLT ===\"\nWrite-Host \"Ort: $backupPath\"\nWrite-Host \"Dateien: $($results.Count)\"\nWrite-Host \"Erfolgreich: $(($results | Where-Object { $_.Status -eq 'OK' }).Count)\"\n$results | Format-Table -AutoSize"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":149024,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":149024,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775863793890}}
