- 6 Daily Notes remain in 01-Daily/\n- Discovered: 6 Daily Notes are empty shells (migration error)\n- Documented in MEMORY.md under \"Lessons Learned\"\n\n### 5. Areas → Responsibilities Migration\n- Moved 02-Areas/ to 03-Knowledge/Responsibilities/\n- Renamed: area-development.md → Development.md\n- Renamed: area-research.md → Research.md\n- Updated IDs: AREA-XXX → RESP-XXX\n- Removed Emojis for terminal compatibility\n\n### 6. New Safety Rules Added to MEMORY.md\n- Rule 8: Migration-Validierung (3+ files sample check)\n- Rule 9: Backup vor Löschen\n- Rule 10: Content-Check bei migrated\n- Rule 11: Dry-Run vor Migration\n- Rule 12: Keine leeren Templates\n- Documented migration failure (empty Daily Notes)\n\n## Discoveries\n\n### High-Value Files in Old Vault\n- **MASTERPLAN**: 800-line integration spec for claw-code + OpenClaw\n- **COMPACTION_SPEC**: Session compaction with ECC memory sync\n- **RUNTIME_SPEC**: Agent loop with Fort Knox safety\n- **PERMISSIONS_SPEC**: Risk-based permission framework\n- **SSE_STREAMING_SPEC**: Real-time API streaming\n- **QUICK_REFERENCE**: Condensed reference guide\n\n### Issues Found\n- 6 Daily Notes in 01-Daily/ are empty (content not migrated, originals deleted)\n- This was a migration error from earlier\n- Need to mark as \"VERLOST\" or reconstruct from OpenClaw logs\n\n## Next Steps (Pending)\n- [ ] Migrate the 6 analyzed files (after user GO)\n- [ ] Continue Batch 2: Other vault directories\n  - Kimi_Agent_OpenClaw Prompt Execution/ (11 files)\n  - Master Rework 06.04.2026/ (6 files)\n  - Root files (AI_AGENT_WORK_INSTRUCTION.md, etc.)\n- [ ] Analyze PowerShell scripts (31 files)\n- [ ] Check for duplicate Master Rework docs\n\n## Decisions Made\n- Emojis: BANNED (terminal incompatibility)\n- Responsibilities: Moved from 02-Areas/ to 03-Knowledge/Responsibilities/\n- Sessions: Strictly separated from Daily Notes\n- Migration approach: Batch-by-batch with user GO after each\n- Data Integration Analyst: Created as new skill (n